project.lock.json

# TypeSpec emitter outputs are tracked on purpose: alpha emitters
# (`@typespec/http-client-csharp`, `@typespec/http-server-csharp`) are not yet
# fully deterministic, and qyl's own emitters evolve with the .tsp inputs.
# Committing the output makes fresh clones build without `nuke Generate`,
# turns every regen delta into a reviewable diff, and caps the blast radius
# of emitter regressions. Regenerate with `nuke Generate` and commit the
# resulting diff; do not hand-edit files under */Generated/.

